subtitleNullable: Turkiyedeki trafik isaretleri icin cok genis skaynakların harmanlandigi veriseti
descriptionNullable:
Dataset Description
This dataset contains information about traffic signs and road markings classified into 24 different categories. The dataset shows the names and number of signs ("nc" column) in each category.

Columns:

nc: Number of signs in each category.
names: Names of the signs in each category.

Categories:
 20: Speed limit 20 km/h
 30: Speed limit 30 km/h
 dur: Stop sign
 durak: Bus stop
 girisyok: No entry
 ilerisag: Go straight
 ilerisol: No left turn
 kirmizi: Red light
 park: Parking lot
 parkyasak: No parking
 sag: Right turn
 sagadonulmez: No right turn
 sari: Yellow light
 sol: Left turn
 soladonulmez: No left turn
 yesil: Green light
 parkyasak2: No parking zone
 arac: Vehicle
 yaya: Pedestrian
 otobus: Bus
 bisikletli: Cyclist
 yapılar: Buildings
 yayagecidi: Crosswalk
 tasitrafiginekapali: Closed to vehicle traffic

Applications of the dataset:
   To learn about traffic signs and road markings
   To develop visual recognition systems for traffic signs and road markings
   To perform data analysis on traffic signs and road markings
